def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('C', 'CP')

print(insert_after_character('ABCDEF')) # ABPCDEF
print(insert_after_character('CCCCC')) # CCCCPC
print(insert_after_character('PQPQPQ')) # PQPQPQ
print(insert_after_character('PPPPPPP')) # PPPPPPP
